1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to law enforcement; to amend section
2 81-1414.07, Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska; to eliminate
3 obsolete provisions; to change the number of hours of annual
4 continuing education courses required for law enforcement officers;
5 to provide an operative date; and to repeal the original section.
6 Be it enacted by the people of the State of Nebraska,
